{"tid":2530924,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"「幫港出聲」成員頻入市 發起人周融1750萬購碧瑤灣976呎","createTime":"2021-05-14T20:50:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-14T21:16:09.000Z","uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"550e1a0bafeeee2fd5f169de2bfd873e3ea51346","tid":2530924,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T20:50:02.000Z","msg":"近月二手樓市持續升溫，不少名人趁機入市。土地註冊處資料顯示，薄扶林碧瑤灣25座高層B室，實用976平方呎，屬於望山景的兩房，日前以1750萬元售出，較銀行網上估價1539萬高約12%。登記買家為周融(CH<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />W YUNG)，與「幫港出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />聲」發起人之一<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />周融<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />名字相同，料為同一人。<br />\n<br />\n資料顯示，單位原業主於1990年以148萬元購入，持貨31年帳面獲利1602萬元，賺幅10.8倍。"},{"pid":"4c204be4e29d8bcaffd07fa4b1f0e64cfadc93c1","tid":2530924,"uid":43575,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T21:08:59.000Z","msg":"呢啲真心愛香港，呢個時候仲肯用成千七萬買樓"},{"pid":"7689e0c6e68c223531eecaa9fcc8f8297564a7fd","tid":2530924,"uid":66433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c204be4e29d8bcaffd07fa4b1f0e64cfadc93c1","tid":2530924,"uid":43575,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T21:08:59.000Z","msg":"呢啲真心愛香港，呢個時候仲肯用成千七萬買樓"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-14T21:16:09.000Z","msg":"真 而唔係走去買美國樓 不過其實可能買左冇人知姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}